1265
01:05:35.650 --> 01:05:37.490
There was already a satellite studio
in Florida


1266
01:05:37.650 --> 01:05:39.970
and now production started
on A Goofy Movie


1267
01:05:40.130 --> 01:05:41.890
at another studio in Paris.

1268
01:05:42.050 --> 01:05:44.970
Rehearsals began on the new Broadway
