1269
01:05:45.570 --> 01:05:49.210
Five years earlier, the care and focus
was on one picture at a time,


1270
01:05:49.410 --> 01:05:51.730
and now there were five movies
and a Broadway show


1271
01:05:51.890 --> 01:05:53.250
in very active production.

